### Search a question [GET /question/search/]
Used to search through the list of questions.
+ Parameters
  + query (string) - The query string to search the database, can be a phrase.
  + limit (integer, optional) - optional used to limit number of returned questions.
  + offset (integer, optional) - used to page and get the next set of questions.
+ Response 200
  + Headers
    ContentType: application/json
  + Body
